Based on https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jkv0pbp0ckQ&t=2559s
- Import anim data
    - pick a first file format (fbx, gltf ?)
- Compress the data (see "An idiot's guide to animation compression")
- Sample the anim data based on current game framerate
- Blending
- Root Motion + Blending root motion
- Animation events, sampling them
- Sync tracks, to sync animations
- Warping